  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/c50cf15ca2474e8d29622a35387de3cb.avif?t=1771447424\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></p><br><h1>Just Updated</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now fully compatible with the Valve Steam Deck. Works great on handhelds: ROG Ally and ROG Ally Xbox, MSI Claw</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/Gear-Steam-Deck-KAZ_edited2_600.png?t=1771447424\" /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>In the distant future, #KILLALLZOMBIES is thrusting civilians into a sport of survival where a ravenous zombie population is unleashed in the name of sports entertainment. With the potential of a collective horde of over 1000 zombies, television spectators vote upon how many and what kind of zombies or obstacles they want to uncage to make survival all the harder for you to accomplish.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/944fb055cbe7b1e9d76593a7e24e50e3.poster.avif?t=1771447424\" width=482 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/944fb055cbe7b1e9d76593a7e24e50e3.webm?t=1771447424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/944fb055cbe7b1e9d76593a7e24e50e3.mp4?t=1771447424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hordes of zombies to fight in interactive changing arena<br></li><li>Live stream interactions enabling spectators to affect gameplay while watching the broadcast on Live from Twitch<br></li><li>Three modes to play: Survival, Local Co-op and Defend the Vault <br></li><li>100+ Powerful perks and Twitch chat commands<br></li><li>Dangerous zombie bosses!<br></li><li>Large weapons inventory and various ammo types</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/b93823ddb376185e2503b60f2d249c1e.poster.avif?t=1771447424\" width=482 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/b93823ddb376185e2503b60f2d249c1e.webm?t=1771447424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/b93823ddb376185e2503b60f2d249c1e.mp4?t=1771447424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/cf5852b438e7bdd579953134380dcc59.poster.avif?t=1771447424\" width=482 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/cf5852b438e7bdd579953134380dcc59.webm?t=1771447424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/cf5852b438e7bdd579953134380dcc59.mp4?t=1771447424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/a425f02acc179b4dd4de2aeb98cdf64c.poster.avif?t=1771447424\" width=482 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/a425f02acc179b4dd4de2aeb98cdf64c.webm?t=1771447424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/a425f02acc179b4dd4de2aeb98cdf64c.mp4?t=1771447424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "In the distant future, #KILLALLZOMBIES is thrusting civilians into a sport of survival where a ravenous zombie population is unleashed in the name of sports entertainment. With the potential of a collective horde of over 1000 zombies, television spectators vote upon how many and what kind of zombies or obstacles they want to uncage to make survival all the harder for you to accomplish.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/944fb055cbe7b1e9d76593a7e24e50e3.poster.avif?t=1771447424\" width=482 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/944fb055cbe7b1e9d76593a7e24e50e3.webm?t=1771447424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/944fb055cbe7b1e9d76593a7e24e50e3.mp4?t=1771447424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hordes of zombies to fight in interactive changing arena<br></li><li>Live stream interactions enabling spectators to affect gameplay while watching the broadcast on Live from Twitch<br></li><li>Three modes to play: Survival, Local Co-op and Defend the Vault <br></li><li>100+ Powerful perks and Twitch chat commands<br></li><li>Dangerous zombie bosses!<br></li><li>Large weapons inventory and various ammo types</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/b93823ddb376185e2503b60f2d249c1e.poster.avif?t=1771447424\" width=482 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/303720/extras/b93823ddb376185e2503b60f2d249c1e.webm?t=1771447424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.